  <front>
   <head>Written in an IVORY BOOK For the Honourable Miss HAMILTON; To be sent to her MAMMA.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-" line_length="9">system this of deep devotion,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-" line_length="9">A Book indeed, without a notion:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And yet in these fair leaves you'll find</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">An emblem of my tender Mind;</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Both spotless, ready to receive</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Each kind impression You shall give.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
